location.fullValue: Aria - Classic Collection Plan, Waypointe of Woodbury - Robert Thomas Homes

data.description:
Welcome to this immaculate villa style home in the Bailey Meadows neighborhood. Featuring one level living with 3
bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage, and all primary facilities on one level. The open floor plan lets in lots of natural light
through large picture windows with beautiful view of a serene pond. This cozy home features elegant kitchen with
quartz countertops, upgraded stainless steel appliances and a walk-in pantry. Only a few steps away the spacious
master suite provides peaceful and relaxing haven with ensuite bath and walk-in closet. The guest bedrooms are
located in the opposite corner of the house with a convenient adjacent full bathroom. Enjoy walking barefoot on the
upgraded premium LVP flooring throughout the entire house. The 15’X14’ spacious storage above the garage with its
separate stair case access provides addition storage space. The high end, high efficiency water softener is owned.
Close to highways 494, 10, 61, and lot of shops in Woodbury. Move in and enjoy
